metadata.name: CannaGod
metadata.description:
CannaGod is a piece that i wanted to release to celebrate the 4/20 day but unfortunately I couldn't launch it on the day. This piece is my tribute to the cannabis culture, a piece made with a lot of details, psychedelic elements and a lot of fun, The main idea behind was to create like a God who that could represent the cannabis culture but with my own interpretation and style .

This piece includes a exclusive print framed and one exclusive puzzle send it to the buyer
